- @header = 'Add-ons'
- @icon = 'beaker'

#page-addons
  h2 For VirtKick users

  .addons.row
    .dns.col-md-6
      img src='https://zerigo.com/images/logos/login_logo.png'
      p Manage DNS records for your VirtKick machines in a single interface.

  h2 For VirtKick administrators

  .addons.row
    .status.col-md-6
      img src='https://dka575ofm4ao0.cloudfront.net/assets/base/logos/common-a4a6ee819f09e95f92bc3cb10d0e6984.png'
      p Get your off-site status page and inform your users and customers about the outage.
    .mailing.col-md-6
      img src='https://mailchimp.com/assets/images/freddie.1403114364.svg'
      | &nbsp;
      img src='https://mailchimp.com/assets/images/logo-dark.1403114364.svg'
      p Keep in touch with your users by sending them newsletters and event-related e-mails.
    .fraud.col-md-6
      img src='https://siftscience.com/images/site/logo.png'
      p Detect fraudulent credit card payments and prevent such orders from being finalized.
    .monitoring.col-md-6
      img src='https://0722ab5fcdecd21847ac-640220752bfc90c9496db9cee20b06fe.ssl.cf1.rackcdn.com/assets/site/logo-main-5e1e655850f6ed46a67ccef0fc4aef47.png'
      p Monitor the health, availability and resource usage of your VirtKick hypervisors.

